Qwt 6.1.1
=========

1) support for shadow builds
2) QwtAbstractScaleDraw/QwtScaleDraw/QwtRoundScaleDraw
   layout issues fixed
   performance for specific use cases improved
3) QwtAbstractSlider/QwtCounter
   fixed for tiny step sizes 
4) QwtDateScaleEngine
   aligning/autoscaling improved
5) QwtDial/QwtKnob
   rounding instead of flooring, when translating values to angles 
6) QwtGraphic
   RenderPensUnscaled flag fixed to respect initial painter transformations
   ( non cosmetic pens on legend icons will be scaled according to paint device
     resolution - f.e high dpi printouts - now )
7) QwtKnob/QwtThermo
   missing updates, when changing the scale draw added
8) QwtLegend
   clipping code fixed in renderLegend
9) QwtPainter
   applying painter transformation for simple rich texts fixed
   handling of alpha values fixed for drawing color bars
10) QwtPicker
   Work around a Qt bug when creating an event filter inside of an event filter
   ( calling the event filter twice )
11) QwtPickerMachine
   Ignoring autorepeat key events
12) QwtPlot
   disabled autoreplot in the destructor
   setPlotLayout fixed
   calculation of canvasMap fixed for disabled axes
   calling autoRefresh instead of update when attaching/detaching a plot item
13) QwtPlotAbstractBarChart
   using layoutHint() as minimum sample width in AutoAdjustSamples mode
14) QwtPlotBarChart/QwtPlotMultiBarChart
   boundingRect() fixed
15) QwtPlotCurve
   painter order of curve pen and brush inverted ( pen on top of brush )
16) QwtPlotRenderer
   order of setting printer properties changed to work around a Qt 4.8 bug
17) QwtPlotScaleItem
   internal cache removed to avoid out of sync situations
18) QwtPlotSpectroCurve
   losing alpha values from the color map fixed
19) QwtPlotTextLabel
   no internal caches for record/replay paint devices ( QPicture/QwtGraphic )
20) QwtRasterData
   handling of NaN values, when calculating contour lines
21) QwtLinearScaleEngines
   trying to avoid overruns for huge intervals ( > max dounble ) in divideScale()
22) QwtSymbol
   pin point translations fixed
23) QwtWheel
   aligning of values improved

   
